title: 16-Pin Package Mechanical Drawing
summary: Mechanical dimension drawing for a 16-pin gull-wing package with top/side views and lead detail.

structured_data.description: Contains package body dimensions (6.2 to 6.6 typ length, 4.9 to 5.1 width), lead pitch details, seating plane references, and detail A lead-form geometry. Drawing revision/date visible: 4220204/B, 12/2023.
